review: She has very good clinical experience and verymuch professional and explains clearly about the problem and make a patient very comfortable.
I had visited Dr sirisha for hairfall. Underwent GFC treatment.  It is soo good to see my hairfall reduced and volume also increased. I developed good confidence.thank you

Dr Sirisha is Highly professional at malkajgiri partha dental.
I recommend her to evryone for dental problems
I had a good experience with both the doctors dr.sirisha and dr.nisheetha.i would recommend this place for hustle free treatments

Dr Sirisha has answered all my questions with utmost patience and gave me the best options I goty dental treatment done and has also taken suggestions on my hair and started the prp treatment iam very happy with both the dental and prp results.

The services that I receive from  Dr.M Sirisha is excellent. Dr.  M Sirisha and the staff are friendly and ensure that I am properly informed about my health and care. I would have no qualms in recommending them to family  and friends.

Dr sirisha is an all-rounder.
**** ******* ** *********** Highly recommend her at partha dental clinic
